{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] it came noticed to the farm, that it's going to Judenrein-- they have to ship them back to the-- everybody to the ghetto, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- there was also on the-- on this farm, there was kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before the war, they used to train them to go to-- to Palestine then, and they used to teach them how to work on the farms, they trained them for the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was about 400 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the head of the kibbutz was a young lady-- Leah was her name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew all the people, we worked together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all went to the ghetto, and we we sent to an area where the people were sent out already, to occupy the houses and apartments.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You went into some rooms, the dinner or lunch was on the table, they couldn't even finish it, they were taken out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we stayed there, the phone lines were still working, so we called, we knew that our aunt and uncle in the family is not far from us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We call them, they said, we shouldn't stay there, we should come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin came and took us where they lived on the [NON-ENGLISH], to the same place where I escaped the ghetto, almost, about the 25, 30 feet from there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we start working, my sister starts working in the factory, and I started working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sisters worked on the shirts, and I worked on the men's clothing-- to alter the-- the gunshot holes from uniforms, pants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I start working, and every time they picked up a few of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they caught you in the street, they picked you up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- right across was the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
